function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.1.15') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.1.15!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '4a37d3d65732c295049efa8138fde7a533ccacda') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '4a37d3d65732c295049efa8138fde7a533ccacda') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '781bdf45651444ce393fd4ef82c20fe997748b71') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '4a37d3d65732c295049efa8138fde7a533ccacda') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('dW50KCRkYXRhWydhc24xaWQnXSkgKyBjb3VudCgkZGF0YVsnaXJpJ10pID09IDApIGNvbnRpbnVlOwoKCWVjaG8gInNlbGVjdCAnLS0gJG9pZCc7XG4iOwoJZm9yZWFjaCAoJGRhdGFbJ2FzbjFpZCddIGFzICRsaW5lX2FzbjEpIHsKCQllY2hvICIkbGluZV9hc24x'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('XG4iOwoJfQoJZm9yZWFjaCAoJGRhdGFbJ2lyaSddIGFzICRsaW5lX2lyaSkgewoJCWVjaG8gIiRsaW5lX2lyaVxuIjsKCX0KCWZvcmVhY2ggKCRkYXRhWydjaGVja3N1bSddIGFzICRjaHVuaykgewoJCSRjaGVja19zdW0gLj0gJGNodW5rOwoJfQoJZWNobyAiXG4i'));
	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('Owp9CmVjaG8gInNlbGVjdCAnLS0gR2VuZXJhdG9yIFwiZ2VuZXJhdGVfd2VsbGtub3duX290aGVyX2FjY2Vzc1wiIGNoZWNrc3VtICIuZGVjaGV4KGNyYzMyKCRjaGVja19zdW0pKS4iJztcbiI7Cg=='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') != 'fa8b7cb09c93abd61901fe21702b16e78c5b1b69') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'fa8b7cb09c93abd61901fe21702b16e78c5b1b69') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'b200116600649d158d58e9258c233c78053f69ca') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'fa8b7cb09c93abd61901fe21702b16e78c5b1b69') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') != '0a5108eeb445b15aafea2501c2b5915d70b3e1ef') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '0a5108eeb445b15aafea2501c2b5915d70b3e1ef') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '9295d9e55a34c2a66f97bc6d441bc526f200fe14') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird') !== '0a5108eeb445b15aafea2501c2b5915d70b3e1ef') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_firebird');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '33f517c021a86a2b957767949f2675eb2d2cab86') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '33f517c021a86a2b957767949f2675eb2d2cab86') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '876eb175ea5c79281a50ad2916be5cb56a7cb0cd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '33f517c021a86a2b957767949f2675eb2d2cab86') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != '349b154075200bdd857a5a65ab1396713696840b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '349b154075200bdd857a5a65ab1396713696840b') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '30725ea58e787d421633a77e9eeb683e0f090ef6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '349b154075200bdd857a5a65ab1396713696840b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') != '1e16017701573e5b457dfd2ef2c8eaa100752108') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '1e16017701573e5b457dfd2ef2c8eaa100752108') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== 'baa3bc654a056cf9388048e6cfbe051966a2a36f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle') !== '1e16017701573e5b457dfd2ef2c8eaa100752108') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_oracle');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	writefile_7();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '0452ce55c1ee704ebbb09e33accd9cc86d5e64c5') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '0452ce55c1ee704ebbb09e33accd9cc86d5e64c5') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '7707ebac1222a38a3fe84dcbf058e5c18ba937ef') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_7();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '0452ce55c1ee704ebbb09e33accd9cc86d5e64c5') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	writefile_8();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') != 'e470f5f5ff1c81773b420843324abae4ca5cca66') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'e470f5f5ff1c81773b420843324abae4ca5cca66') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== '4152f928d231cf185c61583e848d2b7bd2b474a1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_8();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'e470f5f5ff1c81773b420843324abae4ca5cca66') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/config_values.md');
	writefile_9();
	if (!is_file('doc/config_values.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') != '8e1079baa627e0703e36028ba0c43e515dad028d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/config_values.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/config_values.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '8e1079baa627e0703e36028ba0c43e515dad028d') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '1660ca41e08f38650ada070d3d9a3aa7a32d596b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/config_values.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/config_values.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/config_values.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/config_values.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_9();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/config_values.md') !== '8e1079baa627e0703e36028ba0c43e515dad028d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/config_values.md');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_10();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') != '0fa2422a2e9392354932ccaaee0ccbe266d6b219') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '0fa2422a2e9392354932ccaaee0ccbe266d6b219') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '98b47a507c86338fe52150fba42f91bf5893f0f1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php') !== '0fa2422a2e9392354932ccaaee0ccbe266d6b219') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusObject.class.php');

	writefile_11();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php') != 'c2f9299865ee40d0fbc6515f2a399c5ddcc95cc9') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php') !== 'c2f9299865ee40d0fbc6515f2a399c5ddcc95cc9') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php') !== 'ecb7da03c0856858c411c729653c597763d5e5b5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_11();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php') !== 'c2f9299865ee40d0fbc6515f2a399c5ddcc95cc9') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusQueryResult.class.php');

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') != 'd1a8d911f44f4cdc3862a36c2c7e26fb0745287e') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'd1a8d911f44f4cdc3862a36c2c7e26fb0745287e') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'dddb1b2d396f311c55244bcfeef2dcdd85a1e072') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json') !== 'd1a8d911f44f4cdc3862a36c2c7e26fb0745287e') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/902_systemfile_check/checksums.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '61f3e78c5fc2f08f85c105cd9244943dfa417a21') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '61f3e78c5fc2f08f85c105cd9244943dfa417a21') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== 'f07c841b44ac5519677cc8d1e44264cc5d7920c6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '61f3e78c5fc2f08f85c105cd9244943dfa417a21') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != 'c5e575d3d449c2f30b4b474f4a073ccb5b0b7c0a') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'c5e575d3d449c2f30b4b474f4a073ccb5b0b7c0a') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'cb9d1a6edae7751ccacf8698a39433090dae8d14') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== 'c5e575d3d449c2f30b4b474f4a073ccb5b0b7c0a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != '77f13f68d0b87d8b6f77ca2afd65d314f0f85978') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '77f13f68d0b87d8b6f77ca2afd65d314f0f85978') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'e98f66f7719bfca13435e2a85954206de90cbb41') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '77f13f68d0b87d8b6f77ca2afd65d314f0f85978') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_20();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c') != 'c2460025de3d766acd3b5a3e51462e89208a874b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c') !== 'c2460025de3d766acd3b5a3e51462e89208a874b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c') !== '5d440f59aee3b747d55a8ce72fc0542c1f156967') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c') !== 'c2460025de3d766acd3b5a3e51462e89208a874b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/danielmarschall/oidconverter/c/oid.c');
		}

}
